	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_000838_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1'-->
<!-- hand01 and hand02 might be same - 01 is in ink and 02 in pencil--><!-- hand 03 DL 2/6/2/-->
<lb/><p><add place="over-text" hand="#hand01"><hi rend="underline">Insert Title </hi></add><add place="top" hand="#hand02">Explorations of the Interior of Africa 
<lb/>By Dr David Livingston</add></p>
<lb/><p><add place="margintop" rend="left" hand="#hand01"><hi rend="underline">Note</hi>
<lb/>to precede 
<lb/><hi rend="underline">paper</hi></add></p>
<lb/><p><add rend="center" hand="#hand01">Begin</add></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">Pungo Andongo</p>
<lb/><p rend="right">31<hi rend="sup underline">st</hi> Dec<hi rend="sup">r</hi> 1854</p>
<lb/><p><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01"><persName>Sir Roderick Impey Murchison</persName></del></p>
<lb/><p><add place="marginleft" hand="#hand01">small Type</add></p>
<lb/><p><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01">Sir</del></p>
<lb/><p><del type="overwritten" hand="#hand01">t</del><add place="over-text" hand="#hand01">T</add>he letter marked 
<lb/>N<hi rend="sup underline">o</hi> I. is a copy from 
<lb/>memory chiefly, of one I 
<lb/>sent under date of August 
<lb/>last which, with a map 
<lb/>of the country travelled 
<lb/>over, I have lately <del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01">learned </del><add place="above" hand="#hand01">heard</add>, 
<lb/>was lost in the destruction 
<lb/>of the "<term type="boat">Forerunner</term>" off 
<lb/><placeName>Madeiria</placeName>. I had <add place="below">^</add><add place="above" hand="#hand01">The</add> fever 
<lb/><!--hand 03 DL 2/6/2-->

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_000838_0002"/><!--pb/@n='2'-->
<add place="marginleft" hand="#hand02">2</add> so frequently after leaving 
<lb/><placeName>Cassangé</placeName><add place="above" hand="#hand02"><del type="overwritten">that</del><add place="over-text" hand="#hand01">that</add></add> I <del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01">took</del><add place="above" hand="#hand01">could only take</add> Latitudes <add place="inline" hand="#hand01">,</add>
<lb/><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01">only.</del><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01">putting</del><add place="above" hand="#hand02"><del type="overwritten">inserting</del><add place="over-text" hand="#hand01">inserting</add></add> them and  
<lb/>my route in <choice><sic><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand02">in</del></sic><corr>notext</corr></choice> pencil<del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01">.</del><add place="above" hand="#hand01">and</add>
<lb/>I promised to send a 
<lb/>better <del type="overwritten" hand="#hand01">m</del><add place="over-text" hand="#hand01">M</add>ap of <placeName>Angola</placeName> back 
<lb/>from <placeName><del type="overwritten" hand="#hand01">c</del><add place="over-text" hand="#hand01">C</add>assange</placeName> on my 
<lb/>return. <del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand02">by the unfortunate 
<lb/>event above noticed I 
<lb/>am obliged to send you 
<lb/>a sketch of the whole 
<lb/>way,</del><del type="overwritten" hand="#hand01">t</del><add place="over-text" hand="#hand01">T</add>his I shall do <del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01">as 
<lb/>I originally intended</del> from 
<lb/>the last point to which 
<lb/>the Postal arrangements 
<lb/>extend. I have been 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_000838_0003"/><!--pb/@n='3'-->
<lb/>detained some time here 
<w>re-<lb break="no"/>producing</w><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01">my</del><add place="above" hand="#hand01">the</add> letters <del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01">by</del><add place="above" hand="#hand01">lost in</add> the 
<lb/>"<term type="boat">Forerunner</term>". <add place="inline" hand="#hand02">and</add><add place="above" hand="#hand01">and</add> I leave for 
<lb/><placeName>Cassangé</placeName> tomorrow morning. 
<lb/><add place="marginleft" hand="#hand02"><choice><abbr>NP.</abbr><expan>New Paragraph</expan></choice><!--double line indicating new paragraph--></add> I <add place="above" hand="#hand01">naturally</add> feel some little regret at 
<lb/>the loss of <del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01">the</del><add place="above" hand="#hand01">my</add><del type="overwritten" hand="#hand01">m</del><add place="over-text" hand="#hand01">M</add>ap, for 
<lb/>believing it safe in your 
<lb/>hands, I have been rather 
<lb/>free in giving <add place="above" hand="#hand01">away</add> Latitudes, <del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01">&amp;</del>
<lb/>Longitudes and Sketches of 
<lb/>the country, some of which 
<lb/>have been <add place="above" hand="#hand01">copied and</add> sent to Germany. 
<lb/><add place="above" hand="#hand02"><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01">by a german botanist, who is here,</del></add><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01">And</del> I have some Ambition<add place="inline" hand="#hand02"><del type="overwritten">,</del><add place="over-text" hand="#hand01">,</add></add>
<lb/>as I am the only one who 
<lb/><hi rend="underline" corresp="#hand02">ever</hi> made astronomical 
<lb/>observations in this <del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01">country</del><add place="inline" hand="#hand01">part of the world,</add>

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_000838_0004"/><!--pb/@n='4'-->
<lb/>that <add place="above" hand="#hand02"><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01">England</del></add> my own <del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01">Father Land</del><add place="above" hand="#hand01">Country</add>
<lb/>should have the preference<add place="inline" hand="#hand01">.-</add></p>
<lb/><p><add place="marginleft" hand="#hand01">At present</add> I give the following list <!-- strange line symbol connecting text--><add place="inline" hand="#hand02">(see List) <add place="inline" hand="#hand01"><!--can I have intralinear??-->Insert List</add></add>
<lb/><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01">at present.</del></p><!-- check nesting logic--><!-- add link to addspan-->
<lb/><p rend="center"/><!-- What is the line above doing here? -->
<lb/><p><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01"><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand02"><placeName>Golungo Alto</placeName>. Latitude south 
<lb/>9° 8′ 30<choice><sic>′</sic><corr>″</corr></choice>; Long. 14° 59′ 21″ 
<lb/><del type="overwritten" hand="#hand02">t</del><add place="over-text" hand="#hand02">T</add>his is the mean of seven
<lb/>Lunar Observations. <del type="overwritten" hand="#hand02">t</del><add place="over-text" hand="#hand02">T</add>he 
<lb/>residence of the chief or 
<lb/>commandant of the 
<lb/>district is the point of 
<lb/>observation</del></del></p>
<lb/><p><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01"><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand02">About 10′ West and 
<lb/>in Lat 9° 15′ 0 is the 
<lb/>confluence of <placeName><choice><sic>Luinh<del type="overwritten" hand="#hand02">u</del><add place="over-text" hand="#hand02">a</add></sic><corr>Luinha</corr></choice></placeName>
<lb/>and <del type="strikethrough">Lucalla</del><add place="above"><placeName>Luce</placeName></add> Rivers 

	<pb n="0005" facs="liv_000838_0005"/><!--pb/@n='5'-->
<lb/>in the district of <placeName>Cazengo</placeName>. 
<lb/>Lat. 9° 26′ 21. confluence 
<lb/>of <placeName>Luinha</placeName> and <placeName>Lucalla</placeName><add place="inline" hand="#hand02">;</add>
<lb/>3° west of this point 
<lb/>stands the ancient 
<lb/>iron foundery erected 
<lb/>by order of <persName>Marquis 
<lb/>of Pombal</persName></del></del></p>
<lb/><p><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01"><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand02">Lat. 9° 37′ 50. confluence 
<lb/>of <placeName>Lucalla</placeName> &amp; <placeName>Coanza</placeName><add place="inline" hand="#hand02">,</add>
<lb/>on which stands the 
<lb/>fort and town of 
<lb/><placeName>Massemgano</placeName>. I could 
<lb/>get no Lunar there<add place="inline" hand="#hand02">,</add>

	<pb n="0006" facs="liv_000838_0006"/><!--pb/@n='6'-->
<lb/>but I have bearings which 
<lb/>will give an approximation 
<lb/>to the Longitude.</del></del></p>
<lb/><p><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01"><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand02"><placeName>Ambaca</placeName>. Residence 
<lb/>of the Commandant 
<lb/>Lat. 9° 16′ 35″ S. 
<lb/>Long. 15° 23′ 15″ E.</del></del></p>
<lb/><p><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01"><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand02"><placeName>Pungo Andongo</placeName>. the 
<lb/>residence of <persName>M<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Piris</persName><add place="inline" hand="#hand02">,</add>
<lb/>on the South side of 
<lb/>the Rocks. 9° 40′ 35″ 
<lb/>S. Lat. The Fort is 
<lb/>probably exactly on 9° 40′ 
<lb/>the Long. by three 

	<pb n="0007" facs="liv_000838_0007"/><!--pb/@n='7'-->
<lb/>good observations each 
<lb/>giving nearly a similar 
<lb/>result in 15° 33′ 40 E. 
<lb/>Lat. of <placeName>Coanza R.</placeName> at 
<lb/>a point S.S W. of the 
<lb/>fort of <placeName>Pungo Andongo</placeName>
<lb/>9° 47′ 3″. It runs 
<lb/>closer to this<add place="inline" hand="#hand02">,</add> than 
<lb/>that on the South East 
<lb/>viz<add place="inline" hand="#hand02">:</add> 3′ or 4′ distant</del></del></p>
<lb/><p><add place="above" hand="#hand01"><!-- which hand? IT was supplied arbitrarily by me --><!--double underline for new paragraph--></add><del>The above are given 
<lb/>at present as a 
<w>pre-<lb break="no"/>caution.</w> I shall put 
<lb/>all I have into the map 

	<pb n="0008" facs="liv_000838_0008"/><!--pb/@n='8'-->
<lb/>and in another letter to 
<lb/>be marked N<hi rend="sup underline">o</hi> II. will 
<lb/>furnish information 
<lb/>respecting this Province 
<lb/><add place="inline" hand="#hand02">itself.</add></del></p><!-- Following signature lines should all be rend='right' -->
<lb/><p rend="right"><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01">I am, Sir</del></p>
<lb/><p rend="right"><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01">Yours Faithfully</del></p>
<lb/><p rend="right"><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01">David Livingston</del></p><!-- this is moved for printed version to where insert list is but remains here for now --><!-- Page size and paper type changes from this point for next sheet -->

	<pb n="0009" facs="liv_000838_0009"/><!--pb/@n='9'-->
<lb/><p>List for insertion in note from 
<lb/>Pungo Andongo Dec <hi rend="underline">31</hi><!--add hand??--></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">54</p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><hi rend="underline"><!--or is this deleted-->South Latitude</hi></p><table><row><cell/><cell>S. Lat</cell><cell/><cell>E. Long.</cell><cell><hi rend="underline">Remarks.</hi></cell></row><row><cell>Golungo Alto</cell><cell>9° 8′ 30″</cell><cell>-</cell><cell>14° 59′ 21"</cell><cell>Mean of 7 lunar observations 
<lb/>at the residence of the 
<lb/>Commandant</cell></row><row><cell>confluence of the 
<lb/>Luinha and Luce R.</cell><cell>9. 15. 0</cell><cell>-</cell><cell>14°. 49. 0</cell><cell>In Cazengo District. The 
<lb/>Longitude is approximate.</cell></row><row><cell>Confluence of the 
<lb/>Luinha and Lucalla</cell><cell>9. 26. 21.</cell><cell>-</cell><cell/><cell/></row><row><cell>Confluence of the Lucalla 
<lb/>and Coanza</cell><cell>9. 37. 50</cell><cell>-</cell><cell/><cell>Fort &amp; town of Massemgano 
<lb/>is on this confluence. <del type="strikethrough">No 
<lb/>Lunars</del><add place="above">I</add> could <del type="strikethrough">be</del> obtain<del type="strikethrough">ed</del>
<lb/><del type="strikethrough">but an</del><add place="above">no lunars, but I have</add><add place="inline">bearings for an</add> approximate 
<lb/>Longitude.</cell></row><row><cell>Ambaca</cell><cell>9. 16. 35</cell><cell>-</cell><cell>15. 23. 15</cell><cell>At the residence of the 
<lb/>Commandant</cell></row><row><cell>Pungo Andongo</cell><cell>9. 40. 35</cell><cell>-</cell><cell><del type="strikethrough">9. 40. 0</del></cell><cell>The Residence of Mr. Piris on 
<lb/>the S. side of the Rocks</cell></row><row><cell>--The Fort</cell><cell>9. 40. 0</cell><cell>-</cell><cell>15. 33. 40</cell><cell>The Long. from 3 good observations</cell></row><row><cell>Coanza R. at a 
<lb/>point S.S.W of the Fort of 
<lb/>Pungo Andongo</cell><cell>9. 47. 3</cell><cell>-</cell><cell/><cell/></row><row><cell>Cassange</cell><cell>9. 37. 29</cell><cell>-</cell><cell>17. 43. 30</cell><cell>From many observations</cell></row></table>
<lb/><p><del type="strikethrough"><!--don't know who has deleted this-->The above are given at present as a 
<lb/>precaution</del></p><table><row><cell>The Quango R.</cell><cell>9. 51. 28</cell><cell>-</cell><cell/><cell>At the ford, 150 yards wide</cell></row><row><cell>The Chikapa R.</cell><cell>10. 38. 0</cell><cell>-</cell><cell/><cell>Flowing W.N.W., 60 yards wide</cell></row><row><cell><del type="strikethrough">The Chihuné &amp;</del> Confluence of the 
<lb/>Chi<add place="above">h</add>uné and Longe</cell><cell>10. 57. 31</cell><cell>-</cell><cell>20. 29. 30.</cell><cell>Both small streams. Canoes 
<lb/>on the latter</cell></row></table><!--table continues-->
<lb/><p rend="center">over</p>

	<pb n="0010" facs="liv_000838_0010"/><!--pb/@n='10'-->
<lb/><p rend="center"><hi rend="underline">Continued</hi></p><table><row><cell/><cell>S. Lat.</cell><cell/><cell>E. Long.</cell><cell>Remarks</cell></row><row><cell>The Casai (Kasye) 
