<lb/>yards broad</cell></row><row><!-- Row hacked --><cell>Lake Dilolo, source 
<lb/>of the Lotembwa </cell><cell>between  11. 30. 0 
<lb/>and 11. 32. 0</cell><cell/><cell/><cell>W end is 1/2<!-- what is code for 1/2--> mile broad. E end 
<lb/>is said to be 6 miles broad. <del type="strikethrough">the</del>
<lb/>same longitude as Katema</cell></row><row><cell>Katema town</cell><cell>11. 35. 37</cell><cell>-</cell><cell>22. 47. 0</cell><cell>Near the R. Lotembwa</cell></row><row><cell>Lotembwa R. 
<lb/>crossed in</cell><cell>11. 40. 0</cell><cell>-</cell><cell/><cell>Above 100 yards broad</cell></row><row><cell>Soana malopo 
<lb/>Villages</cell><cell>11. 49. 42</cell><cell>-</cell><cell>22. 52. 0</cell><cell>3 miles n n w of the ford 
<lb/>on the R. Lokaloeje</cell></row></table>
<lb/><p><del type="strikethrough" hand="#hand01"><!--block strikethrough??-->The above are given at present as 
<lb/>a precaution (by preliminary)</del></p>
			
